title: Ep 57: Hypnotherapy - The Magic Cure?
description: I've used hypnotherapy for childbirth, weight management and stopping smoking. It's a tool I really believe in and wanted to share with you guys. In this episode I interview my hypnotherapist Rita Black and she explains how this magic works!
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
